We define two helper functions, `forward_substitution` and `backward_substitution`, to perform the forward and backward substitution, respectively. The `forward_substitution` function solves the lower triangular system Ly = Pb for the intermediate variable y, while the `backward_substitution` function solves the upper triangular system Ux = y for the final solution x.

